gomodel:SYNGO_4782  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: A peptide antibody coupled with immunogold labelling shows staining in dendrite and spines (Figure 3). Major staining at the Golgi apparatus by EM and fluorescence co-localization in other figures. Localization at dendritic Golgi is probably more common.. Experimental description: Rabbit polyclonal peptide antibody raised against RKTHIDDYSTWD peptide. Described in earlier paper no documented specificity controls. In the annotated or first paper (PMID: 12393793)." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3185-5709" ;
